<p>
This is a cool park near the house.  Note the llamas.  You can sort of see one of the rivers that runs through town
in the picture.  There's a dam that makes a small lake in it for this park.  Lots of typical houses and stuff in the
background, as well as that castle that I went to earlier up on the mountain on the left.  I really need to go back
to that castle with my camera so I can take pictures of the city by the way...  
</p>
<a onClick = "javascript:window.open('http://www.justinmccandless.com/images/entrypics/CIMG2334.jpg', 'popup', 'height = 750, width = 1000');"> 
