</a>
<p>
Obligatory Loja picture.  This is the clock tower in San Sebasti&aacute;n plaza.  It's in a pretty popular area downtown,
with lots of shops and stuff surrounding it.  The pictures on the base of the tower comemorate Loja gaining it's
independence from Spain. 
</p>
<a onClick = "javascript:window.open('http://www.justinmccandless.com/images/entrypics/CIMG2340.jpg', 'popup', 'height = 750, width = 1000');"> 
